New Features and Important Changes, r0.3 vs r0.2

Author(s) :  Alexey PETROV

2010-02-28

Porting onto the common configuration system
--------------------------------------------
Usage of the common configuration system gives the following benefits:
 - detecting and analysing of the all possible problems and cavates before
   compilation process starts
 - unification of the build procedures 
